344
00:24:05,530 --> 00:24:06,760
Hey, Gintoki!

345
00:24:06,760 --> 00:24:09,640
This one's a multi-part episode, so how about we call it the Bark-Meow arc!

346
00:24:09,690 --> 00:24:11,740
But the Fuzzy-Wuzzy arc is hard to disregard, too.

347
00:24:11,740 --> 00:24:13,720
But there's the Fluffy-Wuffy arc... Maybe the Cuddly Balls of Flesh arc, after all.

348
00:24:13,720 --> 00:24:15,100
Don't bother. It'll end next week.

